1:1 COMMENT "# exhaustnarrow.z - Narrowing-aware match exhaustiveness"
1:57 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "#"
2:2 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# A match need only cover the arms its subject can still hold: arms"
