4:1 COMMENT "# excluded by enclosing flow (an if-predicate guard, a diverging match"
4:71 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# arm) drop out of the requirement, and a subject whose arm is known"
5:69 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# exactly (assignment narrowing, exclusion collapse) needs only that"
6:69 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "# arm's case."
